===Etymology===
Specialised orthographic form of {{och-l|尊|gloss=''[[zun]]'', a kind of vessel}} that inherited the noun sense for "vessel", as {{lang|zh|尊}} became chiefly used for the more abstract senses ({{w|Duan Yucai}}'s analysis of the ''{{w|Shuowen}}'').

